Invocation Name: animal sounds
des:
Animal Sounds is an educational skill that will teach you the sounds a large variety of animals make.

You can ask for a random animal sound, or for a specific animal.

To keep it interesting, a new voice will announce your sound each time.

Here is a list of the currently supported animals, that we aim to expand:
